<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Phone Number Change Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
      color: #856404;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .security-notice {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="<%= process.env.LOGO_URL %>" alt="Stylay" class="logo">
      <h1>Phone Number Change Verification</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="warning">
      <strong>Security Alert:</strong> A request has been made to change the phone number associated with your <%= appName %> account.
    </div>

    <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>We received a request to change your phone number to <strong><%= newPhone %></strong>. For your security, we need to verify that this request is legitimate.</p>

    <div class="security-notice">
      <strong>What happens next?</strong>
      <ol>
        <li>Click the verification link below to confirm this change</li>
        <li>Our administrators will review your request</li>
        <li>You will receive a final confirmation once approved</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <p>If you initiated this request, please click the button below to verify your identity:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="button">Verify Phone Change</a>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Important:</strong> This verification link will expire in 24 hours. If you did not request this change, please ignore this email and contact our support team immediately.</p>

    <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;"><%= verificationUrl %></p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to you because a phone number change was requested for your <%= appName %> account.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@<%= appName.toLowerCase() %>.com">support@<%= appName.toLowerCase() %>.com</a></p>
      <p>&copy; <%= year %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
